get {
  url: https://eth-mainnetbeacon.g.alchemy.com/v2/{{api_key}}/eth/v1/node/health
  body: none
  auth: none
}

docs {
  ## Get Health

  Returns the health status of the beacon node.

  - **200**: Node is healthy and fully synced
  - **206**: Node is syncing
  - **503**: Node is not initialized or having issues

  ### Response (200)
  No response body. Status code indicates health state.
}
